com.infusion.util
Class Venn<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.infusion.util.Venn<T>

public class Venn<T>
extends Object

A class that takes two collections and divides them into three groups: that which is only in the first collection, that which is in both collections, and that which is only in the second collection.
